<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.3.5">
<l>piṇakkaṟa vaṟuvakaic camayamu neṟiyuḷḷi yuraitta</l>
<l>kaṇakkaṟu nalattaṉa vantami lātiyam pakavaṉ</l>
<l>vaṇakkuṭait tavaneṟi vaḻiniṉṟu puṟaneṟi kaḷaikaṭ</l>
<l>ṭuṇakkumiṉ pacaiyaṟa vavaṉuṭai yuṇarvukoṇ ṭuṇarntē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Standing of the path of penance, possessing reverence for the endless</l>
<l>primordial lord who told good things without count, thinking</l>
<l>of the path of heterodox systems of six kinds so that diagreement would cease,</l>
<l>taking the perception of him [and] perceiving so that attachment ends</l>
<l>dry up the ties to be removed on the outer path.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
